-- TODO: generalize to `X : Type v`
theorem rank_eq {K : Type u} {X : Type max u v} [Field K] : Module.rank K (FreeAlgebra K X) = Cardinal.mk (List X) :=
  (Cardinal.lift_inj.mp (basisFreeMonoid K X).mk_eq_rank).symm
#align rank_eq rank_eq
